emergence.strategy.mcts

Class MCTSNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • emergence.nodes.GenericNode<java.lang.Object>
      • emergence.strategy.mcts.MCTSNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<GenericNode<java.lang.Object>>

    public class MCTSNode
extends GenericNode<java.lang.Object>
    This class represents a TreeNode. Important is that there is the possibility to simulate next steps of a node. This has the consequence that there are always father and children states.
